headline: Benchmark Reaffirms ‘Buy’ Rating on QUALCOMM Incorporated (QCOM) With $200 PT
summary: With strong hedge fund interest and a low price-to-earnings ratio, QUALCOMM Incorporated (NASDAQ:QCOM) secures a place on our list of the 10 Most Undervalued Value Stocks to Buy Now. On July 31, 2025, Benchmark reaffirmed its ‘Buy’ rating and $200 price target on QUALCOMM Incorporated (NASDAQ:QCOM). This reiteration comes despite a dip in after-hours trading. […]
